<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[و [فعولة]</span>، بالهاء]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ف]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[التَّنُوفَة]</span>: المفازة،<span class="c5"> وكذلك:</span> التنوفية، منسوبة، قال ابن أحمر <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كَمْ دُونَ لَيْلَى مِنْ تَنُوفِيَّةٍ ... لَمَّاعَةٍ تُنْذِرُ فِيهَا النُّذُرْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[الرباعي]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فِعْلال، بكسر الفاء<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[بل]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[التِّنْبال]</span>: القصير، قال <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>... تَنَابِلَةٌ يَحْفِرُونَ الرِّسَاسا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">الرساس:</span> جمع رَسّ، وهو البئر الخراب.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
